          <div class="parent-info-column-image w-col w-col-6"><img src="/{{directory}}/lv/images/parent-info1.jpeg" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 479px) 92vw, (max-width: 767px) 95vw, (max-width: 991px) 49vw, 51vw" srcset="/{{directory}}/lv/images/parent-info1-p-500.jpeg 500w, /{{directory}}/lv/images/parent-info1-p-800.jpeg 800w, /{{directory}}/lv/images/parent-info1-p-1080.jpeg 1080w, /{{directory}}/lv/images/parent-info1-p-1600.jpeg 1600w, /{{directory}}/lv/images/parent-info1.jpeg 2048w" alt=""></div>
          <div class="parent-info-column-content w-col w-col-6">
            <h2 class="parentinfo-heading">Our Programme</h2>
            <p>Our programmes and practise are guided by the document Te Whariki – New Zealand’s Early Childhood Curriculum. We also have a range of up-to-date documents and research that we use to base our teachings around. In depth observations are done in order to plan around your child and their interests. A range of assessment tools are also kept to evaluate the learning that takes place.</p>
