            <h2 class="parentinfo-heading">Our Health and Safety Policy</h2>
            <p>All teachers at Little Village Preschool strive to provide a safe and stimulating environment with the welfare of the children being a top priority.  Teachers must also take steps to ensure their own safety and well-being at work. A copy of our policy can be viewed in the office along with all other policies. </p>
          </div>
