            <h2 class="parentinfo-heading">Meals</h2>
            <p>All our meals (Morning Tea, Lunch, and Afternoon Tea) are cooked and prepared on site by our centre chef. We offer a range of healthy home-cooked meals for children. We also cater to children with differing diets such as vegetarian, halal etc. Please advise staff if your child has any dietary needs or allergies. Lunchboxes are welcome.</p>
